msgid "emails.requestCollectionContributorData.subject"
msgstr "Request for DEIA data collection"

msgid "emails.requestCollectionContributorData.body"
msgstr ""
"Hi!<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"You have been listed as a contributor of the submission \"{$submissionTitle}\", but we were unable to identify a user in the system with this e-mail address.<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"In order to improve our publication, we collect DEIA (Diversity, Equity, Inclusion, and Accessibility) data from the authors of our submissions through an online questionnaire. "
"This questionnaire can be answered by registering in our site and accessing the \"DEIA Survey\" item in the settings of the profile created.<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"If you do not wish to register, we recommend that you access the following address: <a href=\"{$orcidQuestionnaireUrl}\">DEIA Survey with ORCID</a>.<br>\n"
"There, you will be asked to authenticate your ORCID record and then fill in the questionnaire.<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"If you don't have an ORCID record, you can fill in the questionnaire at the following address: <a href=\"{$questionnaireUrl}\">DEIA Survey</a>.<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"If you are not interested in providing your data, or if you have already filled the DEIA Survey, please ignore this message.<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Best regards,<br>\n"
"{$contactName}"

msgid "emails.requestCollectionContributorData.name"
msgstr "Request for DEIA data collection"

msgid "emails.requestCollectionContributorData.description"
msgstr "E-mail template for requesting the collection of DEIA data from contributors who are not registered in the system"